  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play 7 kinds of games! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for bonus collectibles and extra hidden object challenges! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make matches, find details, memory, montage, and swap tiles, too! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the game in any order you want!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 extra bonus levels! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers and soundtrack also included!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to immerse yourself in an intriguing collection of new games with Just Find It 3! Uncover hidden differences, make exciting matches, challenge your memory, and solve engaging puzzles for surprising twists that will keep you captivated throughout your journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534990/extras/1507e8e2e9d39a10406dbf5227f3ea86.poster.avif?t=1729511675\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534990/extras/1507e8e2e9d39a10406dbf5227f3ea86.webm?t=1729511675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534990/extras/1507e8e2e9d39a10406dbf5227f3ea86.mp4?t=1729511675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a variety of 7 unique game types and get ready for an unforgettable experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534990/extr